<body>
	<div class="container">
		<div id="myNavbar"></div>

		<div class="jumbotron">
			<h1 class="display-4">Plant vs. Zombie Heroes</h1>
		</div>

		<hr class="my-4">
		<h3>Hero <a href="/hero"><button type="button" id="addButton" class="btn btn-primary">Manage</button></a> </h3>
		<div class="">
			<p>Player can choose one of the 16 heroes to play, each hero has its own names, race(zombie or plant),
				action point for each round when in the game, special cards only certain hero can hold, class,
				and a deck of cards this hero currently use.
			</p>
		</div>

		<hr class="my-4">

		<h3>Card <a href="/card"><button type="button" id="addButton" class="btn btn-primary">Manage</button></a> </h3>
		<div class="">
			<p>Card is the basic element in this game, it has many properties, name, race(zombie or plant),
				cost of action point (action points a hero need to consume when it plays this card),
				type(a card can either be a zombie minion, a plant minion, or a trick),
				strength(number of damage a minion can inflict to opponent), health(number of hit points), class.
			</p>
		</div>

		<hr class="my-4">

		<h3>Class <a href="/class"><button type="button" id="addButton" class="btn btn-primary">Manage</button></a> </h3>
		<div class="">
			<p>Class defines which cards can be played by a hero, every hero owns two different classes,
				and every card has a class. Heroes can play a card only when they have the same class.
			</p>
		</div>

		<hr class="my-4">

		<h3>Deck <a href="/deck"><button type="button" id="addButton" class="btn btn-primary">Manage</button></a> </h3>
		<div class="">
		<p>
			A Deck is a group of customized cards, player can build many decks for same hero, but each hero can only
			use one deck at a time. Deck has a property of max card, normally itâ€™s 40, which means a deck can only hold
			up to 40 cards, but this number can be changed in certain scenarios
		</p>
		</div>

		<hr class="my-4">

		<h3>Cards in Deck <a href="/cards-in-deck"><button type="button" id="addButton" class="btn btn-primary">Manage</button></a> </h3>
		<div class="">
		<p>
			Deck contains many cards, and cards can be included in multiple decks.
		</p>
		</div>


	</div>
